        <div class="note">
            <strong>Note:</strong> All values are shown in exact form using fractions and square roots rather than decimal approximations. "Undefined" indicates division by zero. Angles are shown in both degrees and radians (in terms of π).
        </div>

        <div class="key-formulas">
            <h3>Key Relationships</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>sec θ = 1/cos θ</li>
                <li>cosec θ = 1/sin θ</li>
                <li>cot θ = 1/tan θ = cos θ/sin θ</li>
                <li>tan θ = sin θ/cos θ</li>
                <li>sin²θ + cos²θ = 1</li>
                <li>1 + tan²θ = sec²θ</li>
                <li>1 + cot²θ = cosec²θ</li>
            </ul>
